data.description: **5k credit for buyer's closing costs.** 2-story, 4 bed, 2.5 bath gem w/ a spacious 2-car garage + 2 paver driveway parking spots. Enjoy comfortable living w/ practical finishes, including tile flooring on the 1st floor, a spacious formal living & dinning area as well as & a well-equipped kitchen that is open to a large family room. If safety is on your mind, rest assured that the community & neighborhood prioritize security, offering dual gates for accessing your residence. Enjoy access to amenities like a refreshing Olympic sized pool, splash pad, a children's play area, a fitness center, & a clubhouse. Relish the convenience of quick access to the FL Turnpike, shopping, dining, & Baptist Health Homestead Hospital. Life will be a breeze. Only 30 min to Miami & 30 min to the Florida Keys.
